name: Tommy's self-portrait
description: This is my self-portrait. As humans, we are surrounded by so many miracles on this planet, such as love, innovations, living species, and the curiosity to explore. I used two colors from the moon and sun to represent the difference that we experience every day. The sun represents the liveliness and our fresh, new version that we bring to life daily. The darkness and mystery from the moon indicate the deep thoughts, innovations, and reflections that we have after an entire day of experiencing and operating.
